'''Elf warriors''' are rebel elves who can be found in [[Lletya]]. Players who have completed Regicide can receive them as a [[Slayer]] [[Slayer task|task]].{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/713721069136449537|date=26 March 2016|archiveurl=https://archive.is/23AZX|archivedate=28 May 2020|quote=Elves: Regicide quest.}} They are usually killed either as a [[Slayer task]] or to obtain [[teleport crystal]]s which grant quick teleportation to [[Lletya]].
